This is Perl module Bundle::Takuji.

INSTALLATION

Type the following command:

    $ curl -L http://cpanmin.us | perl - Bundle::Takuji

Or install cpanm and then run the following command to install
Bundle::Takuji:

    $ cpanm Bundle::Takuji

If you get an archive of this distribution, unpack it and build it
as per the usual:

    $ tar xzf Bundle-Takuji-$version.tar.gz
    $ cd Bundle-Takuji-$version
    $ perl Build.PL
    $ ./Build && ./Build test

Then install it:

    $ ./Build install

DOCUMENTATION

Bundle::Takuji documentation is available as in POD. So you can do:

    $ perldoc Bundle::Takuji

to read the documentation online with your favorite pager.

